Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.41,0:23:42.28,tanda,,0000,0000,0000,,PENGAYUN TONGKAT
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.23,0:00:04.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhasil!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.36,0:00:05.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Subaru, kamu hebat...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.65,0:00:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang punya ide ini parahnya kebangetan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.86,0:00:09.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh? Reaksi awalmu begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.16,0:00:12.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini sama sekali tidak adil.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:14.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa bikin teka-teki yang cuma bisa dijawab
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.46,0:00:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau punya pengetahuan\Nsoal bintang sepertiku?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.29,0:00:21.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sifat Mastermu itu dipikir-pikir\Nparahnya kebangetan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.17,0:00:24.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waduh, duh, bicara apa kau ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.09,0:00:26.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masa iya menjelekkan diri sendiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.80,0:00:31.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, bukunya banyak sekali, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.09,0:00:33.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi penasaran ada buku apa saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.00,0:00:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Menurut penjelasan Nona Shaula,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.60,0:00:37.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tempat ini adalah\Npersemayaman segala pengetahuan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.73,0:00:39.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitu yang dia katakan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.93,0:00:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Melihat reaksinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.94,0:00:45.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sepertinya baru pertama kali\Nruang arsip ini dibuka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.73,0:00:48.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya kita memang harus\Nmelihat-lihat sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.83,0:00:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang memecahkan teka-tekinya\Nitu Subaru, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.28,0:00:54.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa tidak masalah\Nkalau selain Subaru menyentuhnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.40,0:00:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kalau cuma bisa dibaca\Noleh orang yang memecahkannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.85,0:01:02.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukankah aneh kalau kita semua bisa masuk?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.35,0:01:04.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, benar juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.68,0:01:08.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau sudah masuk ke sini,\Nberarti dianggap sudah dapat izin, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.80,0:01:17.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lihat! Hurufnya meliuk-liuk,\Nsama sekali tak bisa dibaca!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.03,0:01:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buku yang ini juga sama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.13,0:01:22.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini semacam penghambat persepsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.69,0:01:25.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi judulnya masih bisa dibaca, kurasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.23,0:01:27.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini dibaca "Noah Libertas".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.65,0:01:29.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang ini "Aegon Voller".
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.99,0:01:32.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Susunannya juga kacau banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.74,0:01:36.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Semua itu, apa jangan-jangan nama orang?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.15,0:01:40.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, sepertinya begitu, tapi...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.87,0:01:44.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari apa yang kulihat,\Ntidak ada nama yang aku kenal.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.67,0:01:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu, kalau diperhatikan satu-satu\Nmungkin beda cerita.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.05,0:01:49.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya ampun.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.84,0:01:52.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Untuk apa kalau buku tidak bisa dibaca?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.25,0:01:55.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh? Ini kan...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:56.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.48,0:02:15.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Re:ZERO -Starting Life in Another World-\NSeason 4
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.91,0:02:18.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wanita.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.87,0:02:21.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada seorang wanita.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.98,0:02:26.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, aku ragu menyebutnya "wanita",
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:28.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}karena dia terlihat masih sangat muda.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.05,0:02:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Typhon, ayo pergi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:41.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dunia wanita tersebut
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.85,0:02:44.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}terbagi atas putih dan hitam,\Nbaik dan buruk,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.35,0:02:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kebaikan dan kejahatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.70,0:02:49.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sosok yang membaginya menjadi dua adalah
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.40,0:02:51.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ayah dari wanita tersebut.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.41,0:02:58.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memberi hukuman yang setimpal
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.75,0:03:01.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kepada pendosa\Nyang telah melakukan kejahatan.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.00,0:03:07.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Timbangan antara baik dan buruk di dunia.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.50,0:03:10.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itulah yang coba ia sampaikan ke putrinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.85,0:03:16.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, wanita tersebut tidak mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.47,0:03:20.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tak ada tolok ukur yang lugas\Nmengenai baik dan buruk.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.35,0:03:22.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dosa dan hukuman
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:25.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}ditentukan oleh banyak faktor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.78,0:03:27.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lo?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.95,0:03:45.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ma-Maaf, Ayah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.78,0:03:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi jatuh, lalu pecah.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.18,0:04:02.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengakui dosamu sendiri dan meminta maaf\Nitu perbuatan yang benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:12.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Saat itu, wanita tersebut mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.15,0:04:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bahwa timbangan untuk menakar dosa\Nyang telah diperbuat
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.35,0:04:20.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}berada dalam hati si pendosa itu sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.33,0:04:25.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah kau melakukan hal buruk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.00,0:04:28.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau orang jahat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.97,0:04:41.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah kau melakukan hal buruk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.97,0:04:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau melakukan hal buruk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kalian melakukan hal buruk?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.81,0:04:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah Ayah orang jahat?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.88,0:04:59.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah Ayah melakukan hal buruk?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.70,0:05:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wanita tersebut mengerti.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.78,0:05:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ia merasa puas.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.63,0:05:14.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Akhirnya ia memperoleh timbangan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.70,0:05:18.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penyihir Kesombongan menanyakan dosa,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.67,0:05:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}menjatuhkan hukuman\Ndan terus menghakimi para pendosa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.51,0:05:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Subaru!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.05,0:05:28.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ka-Kamu tidak apa-apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.56,0:05:30.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi kamu terlihat kesakitan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:35.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Se-Sepertinya aku tidak sampai terseret.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.63,0:05:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku masih di sini, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.95,0:05:39.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Typhon."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.58,0:05:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apakah itu nama yang kau kenal, Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.05,0:05:44.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.74,0:05:45.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan, bodoh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.87,0:05:47.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kasar sekali bilang bodoh.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.83,0:05:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, tidak ada bedanya\Ndengan buku yang lain, kurasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.95,0:05:53.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Namun, bagi Subaru ini terlihat berbeda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.20,0:05:55.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti itulah yang kulihat.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.38,0:05:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.42,0:05:59.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi kenapa cuma buku ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.95,0:06:02.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Subaru, di mana kamu kenal Typhon ini?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.43,0:06:05.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Susah menjelaskannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.76,0:06:10.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bentar, kalau Emilia tidak tahu\Nberarti memang belum pernah ketemu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.55,0:06:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia ada di Makam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.14,0:06:13.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di Makam?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.05,0:06:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Salah satu penyihir dari masa lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.30,0:06:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia Penyihir Kesombongan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.65,0:06:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penampilannya seperti Beako,\Nloli berkulit cokelat.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.30,0:06:26.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya saja, dia seperti perwujudan\N"Kekejaman yang polos".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tadi saat aku membaca buku itu,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.85,0:06:34.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa itu ingatan Typhon? Kehidupannya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:35.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau asal-usulnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.05,0:06:39.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya aku seperti mengalami kejadian itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi itu bukan pengalaman yang menyenangkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:45.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengalami kejadian ingatan orang lain...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.90,0:06:49.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa,\Nrasanya seperti "ujian" di Makam.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.43,0:06:54.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau itu lebih ke berhadapan langsung\Ndengan ingatan sendiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.73,0:06:56.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yah, itu gampang, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.69,0:06:59.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Be-Benar, itu gampang.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.36,0:07:01.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lupakan dulu sikap kalian yang sok itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.78,0:07:04.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buku yang membuat pembaca\Nmengalami ingatan orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.11,0:07:08.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Artinya, mungkin ini sarana\Nuntuk menelusuri masa lalu?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.90,0:07:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, perpustakaan yang membuat kita\Nbisa tahu apa yang kita inginkan...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.73,0:07:15.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Julius!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.85,0:07:17.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Julius, bertahanlah!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.79,0:07:19.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau dengar suaraku, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.98,0:07:23.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Anastasia.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.42,0:07:25.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar. Bagus.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.47,0:07:27.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tarik napas pelan-pelan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.50,0:07:29.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau baik-baik saja, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.33,0:07:32.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kepanasan gara-gara buku\Nyang tak bisa dibaca, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.23,0:07:35.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa-bisanya kau begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.28,0:07:36.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, duh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:38.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan mengejek.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.52,0:07:40.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Julius, kamu betulan baik-baik saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:41.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.48,0:07:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf sudah membuat kalian khawatir.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.11,0:07:48.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Meski begitu, itu adalah pengalaman\Nyang tidak baik untuk jantung.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.78,0:07:51.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti, kau juga melihatnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.55,0:07:52.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.00,0:07:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Balleroy Temeglyph?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.29,0:07:56.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau tak salah,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.50,0:08:00.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bukankah nama itu ada di salah satu\Njenderal Kekaisaran Vollachia?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.65,0:08:02.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih tepatnya mantan jenderal.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.05,0:08:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dia adalah prajurit berbudi luhur\Ndengan kemampuan yang luar biasa.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.30,0:08:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku pernah selamat\Nsaat duel satu lawan satu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.26,0:08:13.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi itu pun hasilnya tipis.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.06,0:08:14.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Seperti yang diduga.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.81,0:08:19.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya, buku-buku di sini berisi\Ntentang orang-orang yang telah tiada.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:23.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu artinya, buku ini memungkinkan kita\Nmengalami masa lalu orang yang sudah mati.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.15,0:08:26.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Masuk akal banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.90,0:08:29.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu artinya, buku-buku yang ada di sini...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:34.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berisi nama orang-orang mati dari masa lalu\Nhingga sekarang di seluruh dunia, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau benar begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.04,0:08:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan butuh waktu berapa lama\Nmencari buku orang yang kita inginkan?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.95,0:08:46.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang yang membuat arsip ini
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.45,0:08:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}parahnya memang kebangetan.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.25,0:08:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,\Nini benar-benar bikin pusing kepala, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.78,0:08:59.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setelah tahu teka-tekinya,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.27,0:09:02.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau yang tadinya tidak bersemangat\Nsudah mulai tertarik, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.73,0:09:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entahlah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.78,0:09:08.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hanya saja, makin kita tahu\Norang yang sudah mati,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.07,0:09:10.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}makin banyak buku yang bisa dibaca, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.13,0:09:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti mungkin aku punya banyak, dong?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:17.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Buku orang mati", ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Muah!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.91,0:09:21.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuih.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.29,0:09:27.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Abang ini pria yang nakal, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.73,0:09:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Entah kenapa kalau kau yang bilang
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.88,0:09:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}rasanya lebih menusuk hati\Ndaripada Ram atau Anastasia.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.01,0:09:36.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Waktunya mungkin agak aneh,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.89,0:09:39.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku boleh tanya sedikit tentangmu?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.14,0:09:39.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:42.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kayaknya Abang ini\Nkebanyakan tebar pesona, deh.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.98,0:09:45.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan! Niatku bukan itu!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bercanda, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.32,0:09:49.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau memang ada yang ingin ditanyakan,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.40,0:09:51.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kenapa tidak langsung tanya saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:54.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya sudah, aku terima tawaranmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.40,0:09:59.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak kapan kau jadi pembunuh bayaran?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mulai kerja begitu\Nsekitar lima atau enam tahun lalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.67,0:10:09.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi bagiku, daripada disebut pekerjaan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.63,0:10:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}rasanya lebih seperti menuruti\Nperintah mama yang memungutku.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.97,0:10:16.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu dulu, itu artinya...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.51,0:10:19.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh, aku ini anak buangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.68,0:10:22.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku dibuang ke hutan\Nsebelum bisa mengingat apa pun
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.68,0:10:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan dibesarkan oleh binatang iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.48,0:10:29.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Memangnya binatang iblis\Nbisa membesarkan bayi?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.15,0:10:32.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Anak biasa sih, tidak bisa.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.03,0:10:32.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.86,0:10:37.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}sejak lahir, aku sudah punya kemampuan\Nuntuk akrab dengan binatang iblis.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.70,0:10:40.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya aku bisa selamat.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.88,0:10:41.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Malahan,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.30,0:10:46.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}alasan aku dibuang\Njuga gara-gara berkah ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.58,0:10:49.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sampai bingung\Nini hal yang bagus atau bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.55,0:10:55.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, Meili, ini cuma seandainya saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.76,0:10:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.30,0:11:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau di sini ada buku tentang orang tuamu,\Napa kau mau membacanya?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.35,0:11:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang tuaku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.68,0:11:08.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maksudnya bukan mama,\Ntapi orang tua kandungku?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.36,0:11:09.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.86,0:11:11.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sama sekali tidak tertarik.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.03,0:11:13.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Begitukah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.44,0:11:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan salah paham ya, Abang.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.20,0:11:20.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sama sekali tidak dendam\Nkarena dibuang orang tuaku, kok.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.58,0:11:25.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana, ya?\NMereka bukan subjek yang penting untukku.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.79,0:11:28.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.13,0:11:32.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau semisal aku mau membacanya,\NAbang mau apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.17,0:11:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya bakal aku carikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.38,0:11:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tidak bisa sekarang juga, sih.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.30,0:11:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku cari tahu dulu,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan kalau tahu nama orang tuamu,\Naku bakal...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.10,0:11:43.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Abang ini memang bodoh, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.97,0:11:44.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kenapa begitu?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, aku baru kepikiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.23,0:11:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bagaimana cara buku-buku ini bertambah?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.30,0:12:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Misalnya, kalau tiba-tiba\NAbang mati di sini,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.45,0:12:03.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}apa buku tentang Abang\Nlangsung muncul begitu saja?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.74,0:12:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penasaran banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Maaf saja, tapi aku tidak mau\Ncoba-coba buat eksperimenmu!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kelihatannya kalian seru sekali.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.00,0:12:13.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kalian menemukan sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.84,0:12:16.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayangnya tidak, kalian sendiri?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.95,0:12:18.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, maafkan aku.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.33,0:12:21.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku sudah lihat-lihat sekilas,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.10,0:12:23.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tapi aku tak menemukan pola\Ndalam susunan buku-bukunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:27.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sepertinya tidak disusun\Nberdasarkan nama atau kronologis.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.85,0:12:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan kata lain,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.06,0:12:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang sudah kita ketahui\Nadalah kita tidak tahu apa-apa.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.52,0:12:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pada akhirnya,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.70,0:12:40.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}arsip ini rasanya masih terlalu sulit\Nuntuk kita tangani.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:44.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalaupun berusaha keras\Nmencari nama yang kita kenal,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.74,0:12:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}belum tentu orang itu tahu\Napa yang ingin kita ketahui.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.37,0:12:50.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar-benar sulit, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.20,0:12:53.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau begitu, sepertinya
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.92,0:12:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}lebih baik kita prioritaskan\Nujian berikutnya ke lantai kedua.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.80,0:12:58.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Setuju.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.25,0:13:00.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tangga untuk naik ke lantai atas\Nitu ada di mana?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.25,0:13:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak terlihat di mana pun, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.31,0:13:08.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mengingat pembuat tempat ini\Nparahnya kebangetan,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:11.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}bisa jadi mencari tangga\Njuga termasuk ujiannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.56,0:13:13.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang punya?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.23,0:13:15.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shaula!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.44,0:13:16.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sini bentar!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.36,0:13:17.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.61,0:13:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siap! Segera meluncur!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.28,0:13:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Master ingin aku melakukan apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.24,0:13:26.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau melihatmu yang datang\Ndengan antusias begitu,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.98,0:13:28.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku jadi merasa bersalah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.79,0:13:32.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau tahu di mana tangga ke lantai kedua?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.12,0:13:33.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.50,0:13:35.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak pernah naik\Nlebih dari lantai keempat.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.09,0:13:37.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selama 400 tahun?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.34,0:13:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Benar-benar mengejutkan, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.76,0:13:41.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shaula, boleh tanya sesuatu?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.90,0:13:43.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Shaula, kau itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.59,0:13:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Posisimu sebagai penjaga\NPerpustakaan Agung Pleiades, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.93,0:13:50.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Exactly!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.33,0:13:51.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jadi begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti kalau dari tebakanku...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:55.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Empat?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.10,0:13:57.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Atau mungkin lima?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.15,0:14:01.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebuah aturan rahasia milik Shaula
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.32,0:14:04.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang diberikan untuk melindungi menara.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.91,0:14:06.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ada lima, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.78,0:14:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aturan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.29,0:14:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rahasia pula, apa maksudnya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.00,0:14:13.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bu-Bukan begitu, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.16,0:14:15.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sebenarnya aku tidak merahasiakannya,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.88,0:14:18.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}cuma karena tidak ditanya\Njadi aku diam saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.71,0:14:20.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Harusnya itu dicatat secara resmi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.92,0:14:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sudah, ceritakan semuanya.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.60,0:14:25.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini cuma perumpamaan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.76,0:14:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau Master coba keluar menara diam-diam\Ntanpa sepengetahuanku,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.60,0:14:31.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku bakal membunuhmu tanpa ampun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.93,0:14:33.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buset! Ngeri banget!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.48,0:14:35.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bukan berarti aku mau melakukannya!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.77,0:14:37.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Cuma perumpamaan!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.23,0:14:41.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lagi pula, ini adalah sesuatu\Nyang tidak bisa aku lawan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.90,0:14:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Asli, berat banget.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.15,0:14:46.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau memang tidak suka, ya tolak saja...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.82,0:14:50.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bentar, jangan bilang\Nkarena kau punya kontrak?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.04,0:14:54.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau juga roh seperti Beako?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.16,0:14:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tentu saja bukan.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.58,0:15:00.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak terima disamakan\Ndengan makhluk-makhluk lembek
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.05,0:15:01.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}seperti roh begitu.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:03.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pokoknya tidak.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tatapan kalian tiba-tiba jadi ngeri!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:11.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya delapan puluh persen orang di sini\Npunya hubungan dengan roh.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.43,0:15:15.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Terus kalau begitu, kau ini sebenarnya apa?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.31,0:15:16.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau bukan roh,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.73,0:15:20.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kau tidak perlu\Nsampai menaati kontrak juga, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.07,0:15:21.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kamu bicara apa, Subaru?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.23,0:15:24.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mau roh atau bukan pengguna roh,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.65,0:15:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}janji itu memang seharusnya ditepati.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.53,0:15:30.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ya, tadi aku cuma salah bicara.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.24,0:15:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kiasan saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Janji itu penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.75,0:15:33.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ulangi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.00,0:15:34.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Janji itu penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.96,0:15:35.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Janji itu penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.83,0:15:36.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Janji itu penting.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.83,0:15:39.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sial! Aku dimarahi Emilia!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.33,0:15:42.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Gara-gara kau! Sialan!\NCepat katakan semua!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:45.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wow! Tuduhan yang tak berdasar!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.13,0:15:47.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi justru seperti inilah Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.05,0:15:48.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku akan bicara!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.30,0:15:49.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dengan rendah hati,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:53.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}akan kujelaskan secara singkat\Napa yang diperintahkan kepadaku.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.14,0:15:57.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pertama, siapa pun yang menantang\NPerpustakaan Agung Pleiades,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.35,0:15:59.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tidak diperbolehkan untuk pergi keluar.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.69,0:16:01.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baru pertama saja sudah mengerikan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.03,0:16:03.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tetapi,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.80,0:16:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}kalau bisa menyelesaikan\Nujian Perpustakaan Agung
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.28,0:16:08.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan berhasil ke lantai satu, berarti aman.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.65,0:16:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}All ok.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.45,0:16:14.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Omong-omong, kalau syarat ini dilanggar,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.37,0:16:18.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}aku akan langsung jadi\Nmesin pembunuh berdarah dingin.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.33,0:16:20.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Janjiku dengan Master tidak berlaku
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.96,0:16:22.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dan aku akan menyerang.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.29,0:16:24.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Prioritasnya lebih tinggi\Ndaripada janjiku, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.73,0:16:25.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku jadi sakit hati.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.92,0:16:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wah! Aku berhasil menyakiti hati Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.72,0:16:31.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti kemampuanku meningkat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.72,0:16:33.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini pasti perkembangan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.68,0:16:34.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu sarkasme!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.76,0:16:35.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.65,0:16:37.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lalu selanjutnya.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.85,0:16:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Karena bosan, jadi sat-set saja.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.10,0:16:43.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Satu, dilarang pergi\Ntanpa menyelesaikan ujian.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dua, dilarang melanggar aturan ujian.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.32,0:16:51.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiga, dilarang menodai perpustakaan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.88,0:16:55.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Empat, dilarang melakukan perusakan\Nterhadap menara.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.23,0:16:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lima, eng...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.71,0:16:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Yang kelima tidak ada.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.96,0:17:03.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Totalnya ada empat aturan.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.50,0:17:07.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku penasaran\Nyang "dilarang melanggar aturan ujian".
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.80,0:17:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin ada semacam aturan tersembunyi
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.30,0:17:12.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}yang sama sekali tidak kita ketahui.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.40,0:17:15.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu benar sudah selesai?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.51,0:17:17.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berarti selain itu aman?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.75,0:17:18.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sumpah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.93,0:17:20.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kali ini tidak bohong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.27,0:17:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Selain itu,\Nselama aturan ini tidak dilanggar,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.94,0:17:27.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}tubuhku tetap jadi milikku sendiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.98,0:17:28.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Eh, bukan!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.94,0:17:30.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Milik Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.74,0:17:31.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak butuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.57,0:17:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ditolak mentah-mentah!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.41,0:17:35.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi hatiku selalu milik Master!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.87,0:17:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Itu juga tidak butuh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:41.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi tidak bisa keluar\Nsebelum menyelesaikan "ujian" itu...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.87,0:17:44.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Rasanya sama seperti "ujian" di Makam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.00,0:17:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kalau terpaksa dan bisa kalahkan dia,\Nkita bisa pulang, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.09,0:17:52.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Lebih mudah dari Makam.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.68,0:17:55.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Master tidak akan melakukan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.26,0:17:58.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soalnya punya hati yang lapang\Ndan baik lebih dari siapa pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.47,0:18:02.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh! Gara-gara bohong,\Nbadanku jadi gatal-gatal!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.88,0:18:05.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, serang dia, Meili!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.52,0:18:07.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pegang kendali Shaula baik-baik!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Serahkan padaku!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.86,0:18:17.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hei, aku sedikit kepikiran.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.33,0:18:20.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak tahu soal yang buat menara ini\Nparahnya kebangetan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.95,0:18:22.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku terus memikirkan itu.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.00,0:18:25.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pemilihan kata-katamu lucu juga.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.88,0:18:27.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tapi benar. Lalu?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:30.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Soal lokasi tangganya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.13,0:18:32.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan-jangan...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.97,0:18:41.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tuh kan, ada!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.68,0:18:45.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ternyata orang yang buat menara ini\Nparahnya memang kebangetan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.06,0:18:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Nona Emilia, hebat sekali Nona menyadarinya.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Di lantai tiga tidak ada, 'kan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.69,0:18:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya, aku pikir ada di suatu tempat\Nyang sudah kita lewati.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.70,0:18:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tangga ini, jangan bilang\Nsebenarnya sudah ada di sini sejak awal?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.03,0:19:04.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin saja ini juga disembunyikan\Ndengan penghambat persepsi.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.88,0:19:10.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, tidak usah lama-lama,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.13,0:19:12.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}langsung saja kita taklukkan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.09,0:19:13.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ayo, Beako!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.45,0:19:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aduh, tidak!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.92,0:19:16.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Subaru, tunggu!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.85,0:19:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bisa berhenti, tidak?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.77,0:19:30.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berhenti, dong!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:49.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ruangan putih lagi, ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.38,0:19:50.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kurasa?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.59,0:19:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ruangan ini lagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.30,0:19:55.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau ini benar lantai dua\Nyang kita harapkan...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.92,0:19:58.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}"Ujian" seharusnya akan dimulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.85,0:20:01.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mungkin itu adalah pemicunya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.64,0:20:07.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dari suasananya,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.31,0:20:09.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}rasanya ini seperti "Pedang Seleksi".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku mulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.04,0:20:33.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang bodoh yang meraih pedang surgawi,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.84,0:20:35.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dapatkanlah penghakimannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.72,0:20:40.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang bodoh yang meraih pedang surgawi,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.80,0:20:42.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dapatkanlah penghakimannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.52,0:20:51.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang bodoh yang meraih pedang surgawi,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.90,0:20:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dapatkanlah
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.03,0:20:56.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}penghakimannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.28,0:21:04.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Emilia.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:05.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.78,0:21:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang bodoh yang meraih pedang surgawi,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.00,0:21:12.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dapatkanlah penghakimannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.50,0:21:17.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang bodoh yang meraih pedang surgawi,\Ndapatkanlah...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.40,0:21:20.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}penghakiman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.70,0:21:25.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang... bodoh...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.33,0:21:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Penghakiman...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.10,0:21:29.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa? Apa yang terjadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.28,0:21:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Master! Master! Master!\NTolong aku!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.69,0:21:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berisik!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:43.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Suaramu bikin aku\Nyang mabuk ini sakit kepala!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.70,0:21:45.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan teriak-teriak!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.20,0:21:51.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Buset, serius?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.29,0:21:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku rasa kau bukanlah orang sembarangan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.13,0:22:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Hah? Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.55,0:22:04.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Ini di mana pula?\NKalian mempermainkanku, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.01,0:22:06.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tidak, kami tidak mempermainkanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.45,0:22:08.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tiba-tiba saja kau muncul.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.70,0:22:10.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Pahamilah bahwa kami hanya bersikap waspada.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.05,0:22:12.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Siapa kau?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.56,0:22:16.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan sok bicara seperti bawahanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Apa kau bawahanku?\NBukan, ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.48,0:22:22.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau bukan jangan sok bikin bingung!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.15,0:22:23.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Dasar!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wanita cantik.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.70,0:22:28.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wanita cantik.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.58,0:22:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wanita seksi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.75,0:22:31.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bocah, bocah, bawahan, keroco.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.93,0:22:34.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sayangnya aku bukanlah bawahanmu.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.38,0:22:35.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Halah!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.10,0:22:38.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bicaramu itu malah makin mirip bawahanku!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.23,0:22:39.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Jangan tiru-tiru!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.85,0:22:42.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Baiklah, ayo mulai.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.55,0:22:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Tunggu dulu!\NDari tadi kau seenaknya bicara sendiri!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:47.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Berisik banget kau ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.18,0:22:50.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak tadi kan\Naku sudah jelaskan sambil tidur.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.56,0:22:52.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Makanya dengar kalau lagi bicara!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.64,0:22:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Sejak tadi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.85,0:22:56.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Orang bodoh yang meraih pedang surgawi,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.81,0:22:58.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}dapatkanlah penghakimannya.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.83,0:23:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wanita cantik itu\Nbeda banget dengan keroco ini.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.80,0:23:05.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Oh? Dilihat-lihat mantap juga kau.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.36,0:23:08.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Wajahmu itu bening banget, gila.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.91,0:23:09.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Bening...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.49,0:23:12.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kau penguji di ujian ini!\NBegitu, 'kan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.79,0:23:14.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Mana kutahu.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.12,0:23:16.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tidak tertarik\Ndengan gelar dari orang lain.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.28,0:23:19.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kalau mau bicara serius denganku,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.96,0:23:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}coba geser aku satu langkah saja dari sini.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.88,0:23:27.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Kesatria Pengawal Kerajaan Lugunica,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.64,0:23:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Julius Juukulius.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.50,0:23:33.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku tak punya nama untuk dikenalkan.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.70,0:23:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}Aku hanyalah
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.68,0:23:38.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur3}{\fad(00,40)}pengayun tongkat.
